  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist Now!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444290/extras/39a37fc7dbb9ad4a5a063d8a18147c0f.avif?t=1720812296\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444290/extras/cd2d11e3f0bd153609a5764a2b17b0e3.poster.avif?t=1720812296\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444290/extras/cd2d11e3f0bd153609a5764a2b17b0e3.webm?t=1720812296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444290/extras/cd2d11e3f0bd153609a5764a2b17b0e3.mp4?t=1720812296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444290/extras/17222771dcfaf1b8b29b7652d1bc015b.avif?t=1720812296\" width=600 height=121 /></span>           <br><br><strong>Hyper Space</strong> is a <strong>“Dodge ’Em Up”</strong> Arcade game. Collect stars while avoiding space hazards to reach the highest score, unlock new skins, compete with your friends and travel through space to the most distant galaxies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444290/extras/43cdf9df6ab9a35d270cd23b3a3d0f0d.poster.avif?t=1720812296\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444290/extras/43cdf9df6ab9a35d270cd23b3a3d0f0d.webm?t=1720812296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>“Easy to learn, hard to master”</strong> to go further and achieve the highest score you need to drive with mastery. Control your spaceship through a mysterious universe collecting stars and skillfully dodging asteroids, satellites, black holes and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444290/extras/817e3a4e71605a2fe7ac1b412091450e.poster.avif?t=1720812296\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444290/extras/817e3a4e71605a2fe7ac1b412091450e.webm?t=1720812296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast and engaging gameplay.<br></li><li>Score as much as you can with the Arcade-style combo system.<br></li><li>Have fun competing against your friends in Multiplayer VS Mode.<br></li><li>Remote Play Together support.<br></li><li>Adventure yourself in a story mode with illustrated scenes and boss battles.<br></li><li>Unlock new skins.<br></li><li>Chilling soundtrack.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444290/extras/03ae13f3f009ae50a583765f6d6a120c.poster.avif?t=1720812296\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444290/extras/03ae13f3f009ae50a583765f6d6a120c.webm?t=1720812296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the universe of Hyper Space at the speed of light and dive into an intergalactic journey full of challenges and discoveries. <br>Get ready for an experience that will take your piloting skills to new heights.",
