de.<br></li><li>Remote Play Together support.<br></li><li>Adventure yourself in a story mode with illustrated scenes and boss battles.<br></li><li>Unlock new skins.<br></li><li>Chilling soundtrack.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444290/extras/03ae13f3f009ae50a583765f6d6a120c.poster.avif?t=1720812296\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444290/extras/03ae13f3f009ae50a583765f6d6a120c.webm?t=1720812296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the universe of Hyper Space at the speed of light and dive into an intergalactic journey full of challenges and discoveries. <br>Get ready for an experience that will take your piloting skills to new heights.",
